load("C:/Users/Thijs/surfdrive/COVID vaccine/git/Control/NL - control check/.RData")
load("C:/Users/Thijs/surfdrive/COVID vaccine/git/Control/SE - control check/.RData")

df.def.error <- dplyr::bind_rows(df.def.NL, df.def.SE)

df.def.error <- df.def.error %>% mutate(duration.quartile = case_when(
  duration <= quantile(duration, probs = 0.25) ~ "Q1",
  duration > quantile(duration, probs = 0.25) & duration <= quantile(duration, probs = 0.5)  ~ "Q2",
  duration > quantile(duration, probs = 0.5) & duration <= quantile(duration, probs = 0.75)  ~ "Q3",
  duration > quantile(duration, probs = 0.75) ~ "Q4"))

df.def.error <- df.def.error %>% mutate(intro.submit.recoded = case_when(
  intro.submit < quantile(intro.submit, probs = 0.5) ~ "< median",
    intro.submit > quantile(intro.submit, probs = 0.5) ~ "> median"))

df.def.error$duration.quartile <- factor(df.def.error$duration.quartile, levels = c("Q1", "Q2", "Q3", "Q4"))

df.def.error$experimental.group <- factor(df.def.error$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice", "independence"))

df.def.error.NL$experimental.group <- factor(df.def.error.NL$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice"))
df.def.NL$experimental.group <- factor(df.def.NL$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice"))
df.check.NL$experimental.group <- factor(df.check.NL$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice"))
df.def.SE$experimental.group <- factor(df.def.SE$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice", "independence"))
df.check.SE$experimental.group <- factor(df.check.SE$experimental.group, levels = c("no text", "advice", "independence"))

df.check <- dplyr::bind_rows(df.check.NL, df.check.SE)
df.total <- dplyr::bind_rows(df.total.NL, df.total.SE)
df.intro <- df.def.error %>% filter(intro.submit.recoded == "> median")
df.intro.NL <- df.intro %>% filter(country == "NL")
df.intro.SE <- df.intro %>% filter(country == "SE")

set_theme(
  base=theme_blank(),
  geom.outline.size = 0.01,
  geom.outline.color = "white", 
  geom.label.size = 3,
  geom.label.color = "grey50")
